{"tid":1470394,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各位，中共嘅春袋係中國人！！！！！！！唔係外國人！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:58:42.000Z","uid":58345,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"711ad68406a2c1daa2d195711b04aaeedff0f536","tid":1470394,"uid":58345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"我地最大嘅敵人係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共</span></span><br />\n對外國宣傳固然比到政府些少輿論壓力<br />\n不過幕後黑手<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共</span></span>依然唔怕外國「說三道四」<br />\n但係，佢地好怕大陸人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有反抗心理</span></span>！！！<br />\n所以我地必須要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煽動顛覆國家政權</span></span><br />\n大陸人之所以係井底之蛙<br />\n係因為中共怕大陸人知我地只係唔想要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共式管治</span></span><br />\n所以我地要藉今次運動向大陸人宣傳<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共係漢奸</span></span><br />\n要比佢地知道中共對中國人所做嘅一切<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">滅絕人性嘅暴行</span></span><br />\n淨係講六四對佢地黎講可能太遙遠<br />\n最好加上中共近幾年<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對中國人嘅暴行</span></span><br />\n總之目標就係帶出<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反共=愛國</span></span>嘅思想<br />\n類似西九嗰日嘅文宣可以做大佢<br />\n比佢地知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民主自由是個好東西</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星星之火，可以燎原</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時僅記五大訴求，絕不分化割席，不忘721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64945c5dc6fb44cfaf2e2566ec80474ed29c79cc","tid":1470394,"uid":58345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:14:25.000Z","ms